00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,800
We can basically conclude

290
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:14,400
that the victim and the killer knew each other.

291
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:18,040
Moreover, the victim lived in Lienv Cliff for many years

292
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,120
without going out.

293
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:21,660
And Lienv Cliff has very strict control,

294
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:23,640
making it hard for outsiders to enter.

295
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:25,440
So the killer is highly likely

296
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,580
someone from Lienv Cliff.

297
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,560
Besides,

298
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:30,160
there are also some wine glasses at the scene.

299
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:31,960
It should be used for sacrifices to the gods.

300
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,960
I have extracted the fingerprints.

301
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,520
The fingerprints on the wine glass,

302
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,780
besides the deceased,

303
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,820
belong to another person.

304
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,720
Something like an anesthetic.

305
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,600
We must enter Lienv Cliff

306
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,400
to conduct a fingerprint check.

307
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:39,640
But for such a precise

308
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:41,120
and large-scale collection and comparison,

309
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,200
only you can do it.

310
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,800
So we must find a way to get in.

311
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,760
I do have an idea.

312
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,120
How is it?

313
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:11,360
Look closely.

314
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,600
Don't be scared.

315
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:16,440
Come here.

316
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:29,920
What does Young Master Liu want with me?

317
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,940
Where is Young Master Liu?

318
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:38,000
And this lady is?

319
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:51,920
My master passed away last year.

320
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:54,120
The madam swore to remain chaste.

321
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,960
So Third Miss Tu

322
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:58,130
introduced her to cultivate here.

323
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:01,760
Third Miss Tu is generous,

324
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:03,960
and has donated a lot to our Lienv Cliff.

325
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,400
Since she introduced her,

326
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,130
there is naturally no problem.

327
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,840
But this letter says

328
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:11,210
Madam Liu is also related to the Tu family.

329
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:12,960
That's right.

330
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,380
Speaking of which,

331
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:17,320
my madam is actually Third Miss Tu's aunt.

332
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,360
You're still trying to lie to me.

333
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,020
Lienü Cliff is full of widows.

334
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:23,440
The lump on your throat

335
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:26,420
has already exposed you. Do you still want to bluff?

336
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,180
Since I was little,

337
00:16:38,520 --> 00:16:40,160
I have suffered from a terrible disease.

338
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:41,600
With a lump on my throat,

339
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:44,570
I was despised and no one dared to marry me.

340
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:46,480
If it weren't for my husband,

341
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:48,250
I'm afraid no one would pity me.

342
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:52,120
He died in battle. I wanted to remain faithful to him,

343
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:55,000
but I didn't expect that even here they would despise my strange illness.

344
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:56,720
Husband, my life is so miserable.

345
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:59,400
It seems Zhennü Hall won't accept me either.

346
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:04,020
Then I will follow you and end my life.

347
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:08,560
I originally made up my mind to come to Lienv Cliff to join you,

348
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:10,920
but now you won't even give me a way out.

349
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,520
I have such a bitter fate.

350
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,119
Follow me.

351
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,480
Good thing I was quick-witted,

352
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:24,339
or my cover would have been blown.

353
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:42,400
Is this some kind of cult?

354
00:17:43,120 --> 00:17:44,120
Mrs. Liu,

355
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:46,120
be sure to recite it morning and evening,

356
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:48,380
and strictly observe the precepts in it.

357
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,600
Since you are here at Lienv Cliff,

358
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:53,000
you must free yourself from desires and passions.

359
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:55,000
Otherwise, if you harbor any wicked thoughts,

360
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,920
the Holy Maiden will see them and unleash her wrath upon you.

361
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,480
You will be like Gu,

362
00:18:00,120 --> 00:18:01,850
suffering the wrath of heaven.

363
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:03,440
What a sin.

364
00:18:04,040 --> 00:18:06,200
After the sunset bell rings, you must close the doors and windows

365
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,200
and are not allowed to go out,

366
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,600
to eliminate evil thoughts.

367
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:10,440
Violators will be heavily punished.

368
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:12,400
Mrs. Liu, please rest early.

369
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,460
Remember to bathe.

370
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,400
In seven days,

371
00:18:14,600 --> 00:18:17,060
an initiation ceremony will be held for you.

372
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:40,600
I really know I was wrong.

373
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:46,840
It's one thing to be forbidden from seeing men,

374
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,840
but we're not even allowed to think about them.

375
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:49,520
What?

376
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:51,860
Can they control people's thoughts?

377
00:18:52,320 --> 00:18:53,680
That's ridiculous.

378
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,280
They are well-behaved ladies

379
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:58,140
who never step out of their homes.

380
00:18:58,280 --> 00:19:00,120
They come here for the chastity arch

381
00:19:00,120 --> 00:19:01,080
to leave a good name for posterity,

382
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:02,680
so naturally they will obey.

383
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,240
This target audience

384
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:05,900
is filtered very accurately.

385
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:10,920
I finally have a chance to be alone with Mr. Liu,

386
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:13,840
and we can even share a room.

387
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:16,280
No wonder you're so eager

388
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:17,640
to act as my maid.

389
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:22,720
Liu,

390
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:24,520
let me help you

391
00:19:24,800 --> 00:19:26,260
bathe and change clothes.

392
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:28,680
Get some rest early.

393
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:33,000
I can take care of myself.

394
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,260
I don't need your help.

395
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:39,840
I'll be yours sooner or later.

396
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:42,400
You don't need to be so polite.

397
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:43,480
What,

398
00:19:43,840 --> 00:19:45,880
are you afraid I'll eat you?

399
00:19:47,720 --> 00:19:48,840
Spare me.

400
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:50,080
I told you before.

401
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:51,920
We are not right for each other.

402
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,000
Are you even a man?

403
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:22,560
Strange.

404
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,880
Did I see that wrong?
